{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be corporate and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Interactive</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #005f9e;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            background-color: #007bbf;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #cce5ff;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #005f9e;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .game-showcase, .about-us, .contact {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: #e7f3ff;\n            border: 1px solid #b3d1ff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin: 15px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 280px;\n            vertical-align: top;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .game-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 180px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 2px solid #005f9e;\n        }\n        .game-card h3 {\n            color: #005f9e;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n        }\n        .game-card p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n        }\n        .about-us p, .contact p {\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 15px auto;\n        }\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #cccccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #005f9e;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #007bbf;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            background-color: #005f9e;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>APEX INTERACTIVE</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#games\">GAMES</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">ABOUT</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">CONTACT</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"games\" class=\"game-showcase\">\n            <h2>OUR LATEST TITLES</h2>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x180/005f9e/ffffff?text=Game+Art+1\" alt=\"Game 1\">\n                <h3>Chronicles of Eldoria</h3>\n                <p>An epic fantasy RPG with a rich story and vast open world.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x180/007bbf/ffffff?text=Game+Art+2\" alt=\"Game 2\">\n                <h3>Cybernetic Dawn</h3>\n                <p>A fast-paced cyberpunk shooter with intense combat and futuristic visuals.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x180/005f9e/ffffff?text=Game+Art+3\" alt=\"Game 3\">\n                <h3>Galactic Frontiers</h3>\n                <p>Explore the cosmos in this immersive space exploration simulation.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"about-us\">\n            <h2>ABOUT APEX INTERACTIVE</h2>\n            <p>Apex Interactive is a leading video game development studio dedicated to creating unforgettable gaming experiences. Founded in 2010, our passionate team of artists, designers, and engineers strives for excellence in every project. We believe in crafting games that push boundaries, spark imagination, and bring players together.</p>\n            <p>Our commitment to quality and innovation has earned us critical acclaim and a loyal community of gamers worldwide. We are constantly exploring new technologies and narrative possibilities to deliver next-generation entertainment.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n            <h2>GET IN TOUCH</h2>\n            <p>Have questions, feedback, or a business inquiry? We'd love to hear from you.</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Interactive. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}